To Our Valued Strategic IT Partner at ZF,
The ZF IT Finance Management Team is eager to deepen our understanding of your proven expertise and experience in supporting finance-specific applications and processes. To facilitate a meaningful dialogue, we have prepared a set of slides that will lay the groundwork for our subsequent discussions.
Our IT Finance team is structured around specialized product teams, each one responsible for the business capabilities outlined on slides 4 through 13. These teams are also responsible for the applications on slides 14 to 21.
As a first step, we´d like to organize a meeting with your team to explore potential opportunities for collaboration. During this meeting, we kindly ask you to provide a detailed exposition of your company’s proficiencies and historical engagements that align with our needs.
We are looking forward to a fruitful exchange.
Best regards, The ZF IT Finance Management Team
